  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江部落一档写作类节目，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15011/\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0,90,148);\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; margin-right: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江部落订阅本节目！</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>背景介绍：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t语言作为一种文化的载体，文明的传承，不仅仅为我们的沟通交流提供了可能，更成为了我们的精神家园和民族的烙印。然而正是这种传播文明的艺术如今却面临文明本身的冲击，由于互联网文化的盛行和全球化浪潮的加速，弱势语言的生存变得举步维艰。据联合国科教文组织调查，全球7000多种语言中近1/3面临灭绝的风险，全球80%的人使用着通用的83种语言，而最少的语言使用人数仅为6人。<br />\n\t有人认为失去一种语言就意味着失去一种文化思维，甚至比物种灭绝更危险。也有人认为语言种类变少更利于人们的沟通，不失为一件好事，对此，你怎么看？</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tTopic1: What's your opinion on the two views above?<br />\n\tTopic2: describe what is language in your eyes?</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t&ldquo;A cow by itself is just a cow, a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/meadow\" target=\"_blank\">meadow</a> by itself is just grass and flowers, but when they are being put together, they can be magic&rdquo;. Language is such a magic thing with its delicate grammar, elaborate <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/rhetoric\" target=\"_blank\">rhetoric</a> and exquisite words. Language reflects the way we think. For example, Japanese people are conservative, thus their language are ambiguous and indirect, while westerners tend to be more straight-forward when approaching a problem, leading to their language being direct. Diversify in languages brings out innovative ideas more easily than single one. In a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/nutshell\" target=\"_blank\">nutshell</a>, I think it is a more dreadful thing that all people are thinking in the same way than people have some difficulties in communication because of language barrier.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例2：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tPeople are rarely aware of the fact that there even exist academic study of languages called linguistics. Languages are one of those factors which distinguish human beings from animals. We use languages to communicate, to express our feelings, no matter happiness or not,etc. Sadly, numerous languages are at the danger of disappearing as countless languages are dying right now.Taking what happened to Chinese dialects as an example. With the promotion of <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/Mandarin\" target=\"_blank\">Mandarin</a>, many a Chinese dialects especially those minor ethnic groups speak, have come into <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/extinction\" target=\"_blank\">extinction</a>. It is a great loss not only for China but also for the diversity of the world. To some extent, we should take French as a model who pays great attention to the protection of their language.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15011/item/916275/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p699058/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p699058\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p698965/\">李娜的退役告别信：跟娜姐学习英文写作</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p699556/\">乔治•克鲁尼大婚 多名巨星捧场</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p699553/\">水獭潜水帮捡手机 感觉自己萌萌哒</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p672013/\">职场女神：高效女性的七大习惯</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p530074/\">12个Excel基础技巧 菜鸟变达人</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p699749/\">未能同生但求共死 比利时夫妇决定同时安乐死</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p699577/\">日本中部火山爆发 多名登山者被困</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p699783/\">加拿大邮差无法投递 留言门口有熊</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p699828/\">布拉德皮特婚后专访 调侃克鲁尼</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江法语</a>  <a href=\"http://kr.hujiang.com\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江韩语</a></div><hr style=\"border: 0.5px solid gray;\" />", 
