  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p666990/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(128,0,128); line-height: 1.8em;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i1.s.hjfile.cn/entry/201406/c4eb420a-edc1-4d02-9c43-969dc82f4ef1.jpg\" /></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(128,0,128); line-height: 1.8em;\"><strong><a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15399/\" target=\"_blank\">《英闻天天译》</a></strong></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">是一档沪江部落的原创翻译互动节目（</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128,0,128); line-height: 1.8em;\"><a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15399/item/928729/\"><strong>戳去参与节目&gt;&gt;&gt;</strong></a></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">），主持人提供翻译参考文本，对大家递交的翻译作品进行点评，和大家共同进步！本期节目选取的是关于</span>经济影响文学<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">的</span><span style=\"font-family: verdana, helvetica; color: rgb(51,51,51); line-height: 28px;\">一则英文报道，让我们一起在翻译中关注</span><font color=\"#333333\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">。</font></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: #000;\"><b style=\"font-family: verdana, helvetica; color: rgb(0,0,0); line-height: 22px;\"><span style=\"border-top: 0px;\"><span style=\"border-top: 0px; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">SUMMARY：</span></span></b></span></p>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<span>IKEA Is Going to Raise Minimum Wages in All its U.S. Stores</span></div>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n\t<strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">CONTENT：</strong></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tIKEA, the world&rsquo;s largest furniture retailer, plans to raise the minimum wage in all of its U.S. stores by using MIT&rsquo;s Living Wage Calculator, which estimates the base pay needed to survive in a particular city &ndash; a move that could set a new standard expected for major retailers.<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tHuffington Post quotes Rob Olson, the chief financial officer of IKEA U.S., as saying that the average store minimum wage will increase by 17% to $10.76 per hour on Jan.1. Employees at each of the 38 stores will have a different base salary depending on the cost of living in the city they&rsquo;re in, ranging from $9-$13 per hour.</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0,100,0);\"><strong>【沪江英语小编】</strong></span>大家在查看主持人提供的翻译版本前，可以先自己进行尝试翻译练习，只有在不断的翻译中翻译能力才能有所提升哦！<br />\n\t轻松注册沪江，马上参与<a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15399/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>【英闻天天译】</strong></a>节目练翻译&rarr;<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15399/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/810ca373cf4442a188b39dd8ff64425f.jpg\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>本期节目参考译文：</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(128,128,128);\">（参考译文由该节目主持人提供，仅供参考，欢迎大家讨论）</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: #000;\"><strong>参考译文1：</strong></span></p>\n<div class=\"replyview red\">\n\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span style=\"color: #000;\">宜家家居，世界上最大的家具零售商，打算使用麻省理工大学研制的生存薪水计算器在其美国所有的卖点内提高最低工资，该工具估算出在某个城市生存所需要的最少的花费，宜家此举可以帮助零售商们建立新的预期标准。<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t《赫芬顿邮报》引用美国宜家的首席财政官罗伯&middot;奥尔森的话，他说一月一日商店最低工资的平均值会增长17% 至每小时10.76美元。38家商店里的员工将享受一个新的与他们居住城市的基本花费相挂钩的基础薪金，每小时9-13 美元左右。</span></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span style=\"color: #000;\"><span style=\"color: #000;\"><strong>参考译文2：</strong></span></span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"replyview red\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span style=\"color: #000;\"><span style=\"color: #000;\">世界上最大的家俱零售商&ldquo;宜家&rdquo;，计划提高美国所有门店的最低工资，此举可能为各大零售商设置了一个预期工资的新标准。该公司使用麻省理工学院的&ldquo;生活工资计算器&rdquo;来估算在某个城市生活所需的基本工资<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t《赫芬顿邮报》援引美国宜家首席财务官罗布&bull;奥尔森的话称，门店平均最低工资从1月1日起将提高17%，达到每小时10.76美元。38家门店的所有员工将根据他们所在城市的生活成本，得到不同的基本工资，每小时9-13美元不等。</span></span></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t