  "link": "http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p664547/", 
  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p664547/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://365jilin.com/uploads/allimg/130212/1294-130212150920.jpg\" style=\"width: 400px; height: 265px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p664547\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\tStaying in Europe, Pope Benedict XVI's shock decision to resign has led to a huge <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/outpouring\" target=\"_blank\">outpouring</a> of emotion from Roman Catholics all over the world. The 85-year-old <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/pope\" target=\"_blank\">pope</a> gave his advancing years and failing faculties as the reason for what many people <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/perceive\" target=\"_blank\">perceive</a> to be a premature departure. But some critics believe the issue of clerical sexual abuse, which the pope has had to deal with throughout his career, could be another reason for his decision. By sheer coincidence, it's the subject of a new <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/documentary\" target=\"_blank\">documentary</a> that has just been released. Here's an <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/extract\" target=\"_blank\">extract</a> from the film's <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/trailer\" target=\"_blank\">trailer</a>.</p>\n<p>\n\t&quot;When a man is ordained a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/priest\" target=\"_blank\">priest</a>, he is changed ontologically. He is made a different brand of human being, a little less than the angels.&quot;</p>\n<p>\n\t&quot;When I first entered St. Johns, I loved it. In the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/confessional\" target=\"_blank\">confessional</a> <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/booth\" target=\"_blank\">booth</a>, there was a dividing wall. But there was a little space, so you could sign back and forth. And he would bless you. And he told me to take off my pants. I kept it a secret.&quot;</p>\n<p>\n\tVoices and sounds there from the new documentary film Mea Maxima Culpa: Silence in the House of God by the Oscar-winning director Alex Gibney. The film focuses on how the Roman Catholic church has dealt with allegations of sexual abuse by priests over the past 50 years or so.</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: #808080;\">声明：音视频均来自互联网链接，仅供学习使用。本网站自身不存储、控制、修改被链接的内容。&ldquo;沪江英语&rdquo;高度重视知识产权保护。当如发现本网站发布的信息包含有侵犯其著作权的链接内容时，请联系我们，我们将依法采取措施移除相关内容或屏蔽相关链接。&nbsp;</span></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p664547/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p664547\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p698965/\">李娜的退役告别信：跟娜姐学习英文写作</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p699556/\">乔治•克鲁尼大婚 多名巨星捧场</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p699553/\">水獭潜水帮捡手机 感觉自己萌萌哒</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p672013/\">职场女神：高效女性的七大习惯</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p530074/\">12个Excel基础技巧 菜鸟变达人</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p699749/\">未能同生但求共死 比利时夫妇决定同时安乐死</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p699577/\">日本中部火山爆发 多名登山者被困</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p699783/\">加拿大邮差无法投递 留言门口有熊</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p699828/\">布拉德皮特婚后专访 调侃克鲁尼</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江法语</a>  <a href=\"http://kr.hujiang.com\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江韩语</a></div><hr style=\"border: 0.5px solid gray;\" />", 
