  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p664530/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://npaper.dtnews.cn/File/upfile/2013-02-17-03-44-04.jpg\" style=\"width: 400px; height: 289px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p664530\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\tBut first, a meteor thought to weigh ten tonnes has sent <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/blazing\" target=\"_blank\">blazing</a> <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/fragment\" target=\"_blank\">fragments</a> across the sky over the southern Urals in Russia causing a series of <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/blast\" target=\"_blank\">blasts</a>. As many as 1,000 people are reported to have been injured, many cut by <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/shattered\" target=\"_blank\">shattered</a> glass. Officials said the meteor caused damage in six cities. Video pictures showed a white condensation trail streaking overhead followed by an intense white flash. The Russian space agency Roscosmos said the meteor pieces travelled at speeds of up to 30 kilometres a second. The meteor caused a series of <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/explosion\" target=\"_blank\">explosions</a> setting off a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/chorus\" target=\"_blank\">chorus</a> of car alarms.</p>\n<p>\n\tThis woman, Daria Fantova, told the BBC what happened to her.</p>\n<p>\n\t&quot;I was awoken in the morning by a really loud sound. It sounded like an explosion, and so I ran to the balcony to see what was happening. And I saw a light line in the sky. It was crossing the sky right above my house. And so I thought it was the plane crash, then I thought that was maybe a rocket launching. Outside there, windows were broken, the balconies were broken, people were running around.&quot;</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: #808080;\">声明：音视频均来自互联网链接，仅供学习使用。本网站自身不存储、控制、修改被链接的内容。&ldquo;沪江英语&rdquo;高度重视知识产权保护。当如发现本网站发布的信息包含有侵犯其著作权的链接内容时，请联系我们，我们将依法采取措施移除相关内容或屏蔽相关链接。</span></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p664530/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p664530\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p698965/\">李娜的退役告别信：跟娜姐学习英文写作</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p699556/\">乔治•克鲁尼大婚 多名巨星捧场</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p699553/\">水獭潜水帮捡手机 感觉自己萌萌哒</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p672013/\">职场女神：高效女性的七大习惯</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p530074/\">12个Excel基础技巧 菜鸟变达人</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p699749/\">未能同生但求共死 比利时夫妇决定同时安乐死</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p699577/\">日本中部火山爆发 多名登山者被困</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p699783/\">加拿大邮差无法投递 留言门口有熊</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p699828/\">布拉德皮特婚后专访 调侃克鲁尼</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" st